Greatest Hits is the third Springsteen hits comp to appear in America and the first to be billed to Bruce & the E Street Band. nine big hits from the golden age of classic rock "Rosalita" through "Born in the U.S.A."  with two cuts from The Rising and "Radio Nowhere" added for good measure.
